HEADWORD: handlock
<hw>handlock</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a metal loop that can be locked
around the wrist, usually used in pairs; a handcuff.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> handcuffs, handcuff, cuffs, cuff, manacle.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

